54
00:05:48,343 --> 00:05:50,655
Does that mean we can meet
Ms. Na Hye Sung in person?

55
00:05:50,776 --> 00:05:52,043
I can't wait.

56
00:05:52,151 --> 00:05:53,359
It sounds fun.

57
00:05:53,443 --> 00:05:55,460
