by putting on an act.

62
00:06:06,526 --> 00:06:09,008
Did you just say "seduce"?

63
00:06:09,610 --> 00:06:12,331
That word really doesn't suit you.

64
00:06:12,431 --> 00:06:13,535
Hey.

65
00:06:15,219 --> 00:06:16,526
