much on the same level.

87
00:07:36,276 --> 00:07:37,878
We're both tall as well.

88
00:07:38,443 --> 00:07:40,044
Do you have any conscience at all?

89
00:07:45,246 --> 00:07:47,943
I'm sure you all know who she is, but
I'll still introduce her to you.

90
00:07:48,043 --> 00:07:50,828
She's a proud graduate of Hankook
University's chemistry department,

91
00:07:50,943 --> 00:07:52,856
and the CEO of Kelun Korea.
She's Ms. Na Hye Sung.

92
00:07:56,843 --> 00:07:59,243
I'm glad to meet you all.
My name is Na Hye Sung.

93
00:08:06,518 --> 00:08:08,430
Where's Kyung Seok?

94
00:08:08,874 --> 00:08:10,177
His mom came to school...

95
00:08:10,265 --> 00:08:12,880
...to do a lecture,
but he's not even here.

96
00:08:18,943 --> 00:08:21,337
Our manager desperately
waited for you to come,

97
00:08:21,437 --> 00:08:23,852
but he went to a seminar abroad.

98
00:08:24,343 --> 00:08:27,695
I might not be as good as him,
but can I still give it a try?

99
00:08:27,795 --> 00:08:30,793
I don't care as long as you pay me.

100
00:08:31,109 --> 00:08:32,902
Thank you for trusting me.

101
00:08:33,002 --> 00:08:34,215
Do I get paid right away?

102
00:08:34,315 --> 00:08:36,643
Yes, you'll get paid
as soon as you're done.

103
00:08:36,844 --> 00:08:38,544
Let's begin.

104
00:08:42,448 --> 00:08:44,443
You have a girlfriend, right?

105
00:08:44,576 --> 00:08:46,844
I hope she'll like it.

106
00:08:46,943 --> 00:08:50,444
But then again, it must not matter
since you're so good-looking.

107
00:08:50,543 --> 00:08:53,244
Even an afro would look like
a fashion trend on you.

108
00:08:56,543 --> 00:08:59,418
What I meant to say is
that a person's look...

109
00:08:59,518 --> 00:09:02,828
...is what actually
completes the hairstyle.

110
00:09:02,943 --> 00:09:05,744
I won't do an afro on you. I'm not crazy.

111
00:09:06,251 --> 00:09:09,029
Perfume always comes last.

112
00:09:09,242 --> 00:09:12,058
Let me explain. When you
get ready to go out,

113
00:09:12,142 --> 00:09:14,453
you put on your clothes,
do your hair, and put makeup on.

114
00:09:14,553 --> 00:09:17,843
And nobody puts on perfume before
doing any of those things.

115
00:09:17,977 --> 00:09:20,755
However, there are times when
this invisible last step...

116
00:09:20,855 --> 00:09:23,445
...ends up lingering in people's
memories for a very long time.

117
00:09:23,576 --> 00:09:26,477
It's hard to remember a
certain person's hairstyle,

118
00:09:26,576 --> 00:09:28,559
or outfit from a long time ago.

119
00:09:28,743 --> 00:09:30,682
But you do remember their smell,

120
00:09:30,782 --> 00:09:32,859
and that stays in your head
along with that person's image.

121
00:09:38,991 --> 00:09:40,081
This is yours, isn't it?

122
00:09:41,871 --> 00:09:43,483
You can wear that perfume.

123
00:09:46,485 --> 00:09:48,675
When you smell the steam coming
from a new batch of rice,

124
00:09:48,776 --> 00:09:50,885
you're reminded of your
mother who lives back home.

125
00:09:51,142 --> 00:09:54,261
And when you smell the perfume you
used to wear a long time ago,

126
00:09:54,376 --> 00:09:56,392
you're reminded of how you
used to feel back then.

127
00:09:57,691 --> 00:09:59,701
I'm not sure...

128
00:09:59,796 --> 00:10:02,497
...how you'll remember me...

129
00:10:13,173 --> 00:10:15,337
That's Kyung Seok.

130
00:10:15,535 --> 00:10:18,852
I have to say, he kind of puts
himself in the spotlight.

131
00:10:36,142 --> 00:10:40,027
I'm not sure how you'll
remember me after this lecture.

132
00:10:40,142 --> 00:10:42,809
- Don't ever dye your hair like him.
- But I hope...

133
00:10:42,921 --> 00:10:43,909
you'll at least remember...

134
00:10:44,027 --> 00:10:46,814
- It doesn't look good on him.
- What I told you about scent.

135
00:10:47,409 --> 00:10:50,523
If you wish to take part
in our company program,

136
00:10:50,643 --> 00:10:52,441
please send in your applications.

137
00:10:52,525 --> 00:10:54,647
