144
00:11:19,621 --> 00:11:20,742
Well...

145
00:11:21,343 --> 00:11:22,643
What's your plan for the summer?

146
00:11:22,835 --> 00:11:24,359
Are you going to apply for the program?

147
00:11:26,599 --> 00:11:27,799
I'll think about it.

148
00:11:28,209 --> 00:11:31,011
Okay, but I hope you do apply.

149
00:11:34,276 --> 00:11:35,257
I'll see you.

150
00:11:40,966 --> 00:11:42,978
Is he going through late adolescence?

151
00:11:43,984 --> 00:11:45,083
What's up with him?

152
00:11:46,765 --> 00:11:49,777
