they go through a break up.

153
00:11:49,982 --> 00:11:51,494
I wonder if it's something similar.

154
00:11:58,643 --> 00:11:59,659
Sorry.

155
00:12:07,381 --> 00:12:09,477
You dyed your hair.

156
00:12:11,353 --> 00:12:12,373
Yes.

157
00:12:13,876 --> 00:12:16,176
- It looks pretty.
- I didn't do it to look pretty.

158
00:12:16,787 --> 00:12:19,359
Oh, sorry. It looks great.

159
00:12:19,443 --> 00:12:21,061
I didn't do it to look great.

160
00:12:21,343 --> 00:12:24,153
Oh, really? Then I guess you
just did it for no reason.

161
00:12:24,276 --> 00:12:25,869
Not exactly.

162
00:12:27,899 --> 00:12:30,025
Well, okay.

163
00:12:30,125 --> 00:12:33,232
I'll go now. See you.
Good luck on your exams.

164
00:12:35,510 --> 00:12:38,310
