The exams haven't even started yet.

165
00:12:38,409 --> 00:12:40,409
This is driving me crazy.

166
00:12:44,490 --> 00:12:46,182
Do you think he's getting
ready to become a celebrity?

167
00:12:46,576 --> 00:12:48,280
