fit to be a celebrity.

168
00:12:48,380 --> 00:12:50,465
What's wrong with
Kyung Seok's personality?

169
00:12:51,690 --> 00:12:53,278
It's not normal.

170
00:12:53,476 --> 00:12:55,192
