176
00:13:11,810 --> 00:13:13,042
I'm done.

177
00:13:14,943 --> 00:13:19,126
But he's too good-looking
to erase from my heart.

178
00:13:19,943 --> 00:13:23,788
I know you guys also have a
small crush on him as well.

179
00:13:24,409 --> 00:13:25,404
Aren't I correct?

180
00:13:40,612 --> 00:13:43,715
Be honest with me. My cooking
was terrible, wasn't it?

181
00:13:47,413 --> 00:13:49,576
