182
00:13:50,209 --> 00:13:52,676
It wasn't that bad.

183
00:13:54,300 --> 00:13:58,221
By the way, Kyung Hee.
Will you take a look at this?

184
00:14:03,010 --> 00:14:05,005
- Is that Kyung Seok?
- Yes.

185
00:14:05,409 --> 00:14:07,325
I didn't want to sound too nagging,

186
