why he dyed his hair.

187
00:14:10,309 --> 00:14:12,935
He's not the type who
cares about how he looks.

188
00:14:13,116 --> 00:14:14,322
I wonder what's gotten into him.

189
00:14:15,409 --> 00:14:16,655
