193
00:14:32,927 --> 00:14:34,195
Thanks.

194
00:14:35,610 --> 00:14:36,907
I want you to write me a receipt.

195
00:14:38,779 --> 00:14:40,693
You said a verbal agreement
wouldn't be effective.

196
00:14:41,782 --> 00:14:43,901
I see you've gotten used to
the life in the society now.

197
00:14:44,022 --> 00:14:45,721
Didn't I say that I learn
everything quickly?

198
00:14:45,843 --> 00:14:47,533
It's partly thanks to my useful tips.

199
00:14:47,643 --> 00:14:49,332
