200
00:14:52,343 --> 00:14:54,951
- How cool of you.
- Aren't you writing me a receipt?

201
00:15:02,117 --> 00:15:03,725
Did you do a modeling for a hair salon?

202
00:15:05,309 --> 00:15:06,709
