203
00:15:07,022 --> 00:15:08,921
I told you I've done almost
every part-time job.

204
00:15:09,021 --> 00:15:10,377
(Do Kyung Seok has paid...)

205
00:15:10,486 --> 00:15:12,272
I thought you wouldn't do such thing
with your personality.

206
00:15:12,357 --> 00:15:13,857
Did you not like doing
house chores that much?

207
00:15:14,879 --> 00:15:18,070
Or did you have a change in mind?

208
00:15:22,375 --> 00:15:24,651
Don't act like you know
everything about me.

209
00:16:30,506 --> 00:16:32,506
He changed back his hair color.

210
00:17:39,924 --> 00:17:42,024
I got this question wrong.

211
00:17:42,109 --> 00:17:46,436
