about we go play games?

213
00:17:51,318 --> 00:17:53,415
Deal. Let's get it.

214
00:17:53,530 --> 00:17:54,625
Let's go.

215
00:17:55,710 --> 00:17:57,504
I'm free.

216
00:17:57,799 --> 00:17:59,895
Why don't we go eat something delicious?

217
00:17:59,995 --> 00:18:02,811
Let's not eat near school.
I want to go somewhere far away.

218
00:18:02,899 --> 00:18:04,790
Let's go.

219
00:18:05,127 --> 00:18:06,142
Let's go.

220
00:18:12,114 --> 00:18:13,732
Hello, Ms. Na.

221
00:18:15,296 --> 00:18:17,912
Yes, I'm done with my finals.

222
00:18:21,398 --> 00:18:22,500
Okay.

223
00:18:23,874 --> 00:18:25,375
Didn't I gain weight?

224
00:18:25,785 --> 00:18:28,382
