227
00:18:32,417 --> 00:18:33,731
How did you do on your finals?

228
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:36,041
- Hello.
- Hi.

229
00:18:36,147 --> 00:18:39,747
About going on a field trip to
Kyung Seok's mother's company...

230
00:18:40,227 --> 00:18:41,678
Are there senior applicants?

231
00:18:41,874 --> 00:18:44,575
- Not that I know of.
- Is that right?

232
00:18:44,889 --> 00:18:46,289
It might be quite awkward then.

233
00:18:46,373 --> 00:18:47,795
Are you going to apply for it?

234
00:18:49,367 --> 00:18:52,028
Never mind, it wouldn't look
good for me to be there.

235
00:18:54,741 --> 00:18:56,030
Are you still sulky?

236
00:18:57,240 --> 00:18:59,706
Goodness. Bye.

237
00:18:59,807 --> 00:19:00,821
Bye.

238
00:19:02,240 --> 00:19:04,907
- What did you just do?
- What?

239
00:19:05,006 --> 00:19:07,006
Don't you know that he spoke
ill of me for being fat?

240
00:19:07,106 --> 00:19:09,291
How could you talk with him
like nothing happened?

241
00:19:09,391 --> 00:19:11,874
But it's not like I'm never
going to see him again.

242
00:19:12,607 --> 00:19:15,780
Kyung Seok turned him into a mop.

243
00:19:15,907 --> 00:19:17,342
Even classmates care for each other.

244
00:19:17,474 --> 00:19:18,748
What's up with you?

245
00:19:19,858 --> 00:19:20,874
Tae Hee.

246
00:19:22,245 --> 00:19:24,252
Tae Hee, let's go eat something delicious.

247
00:19:25,275 --> 00:19:26,019
Tae...

248
00:19:26,907 --> 00:19:28,417
Gosh, it's tiring.

249
00:19:36,408 --> 00:19:38,937
Dong Won, you must've been really hungry.

250
00:19:39,941 --> 00:19:43,126
Sorry I couldn't take care of you
because I was busy with my finals.

251
00:19:44,474 --> 00:19:45,573
Is it good?

252
00:19:51,266 --> 00:19:52,865
Hi, Dong Won.

253
00:19:55,874 --> 00:19:57,546
Guys, I think...

254
00:19:57,646 --> 00:20:00,277
...the beauty in my department
really has a crush on me.

255
00:20:00,377 --> 00:20:02,081
That's only your delusion.

256
00:20:02,181 --> 00:20:05,479
No, I'm telling you.
The name of her cat...

257
