...is the same with my name.

258
00:20:08,096 --> 00:20:10,757
Maybe your name is Na Bi or Kitty.

259
00:20:10,857 --> 00:20:13,040
It's rarely used to name a cat.

260
00:20:13,153 --> 00:20:14,643
It's for people.

261
00:20:15,136 --> 00:20:16,864
Can this be a coincidence?

262
00:20:17,373 --> 00:20:19,327
Can you still say that
she doesn't like me?

263
00:20:27,407 --> 00:20:29,464
It must've been hard
studying for your finals.

264
00:20:29,739 --> 00:20:30,946
Eat up.

265
00:20:31,328 --> 00:20:32,941
Thank you.

266
00:20:35,740 --> 00:20:36,840
Let me do it.

267
00:20:36,929 --> 00:20:39,428
Moms usually do this kind of stuff.

268
00:20:39,528 --> 00:20:40,745
Eat up already.

269
00:20:41,841 --> 00:20:43,733
Thank you.

270
00:20:46,897 --> 00:20:50,201
By the way, didn't you want
to say something to me?

271
00:20:52,995 --> 00:20:55,506
Actually, I have a question.

272
00:20:56,801 --> 00:21:00,183
Nothing special has happened
to Kyung Seok, right?

273
00:21:03,273 --> 00:21:06,384
I don't think so.

274
00:21:07,683 --> 00:21:09,787
Then why did he do that to his hair?

275
00:21:09,907 --> 00:21:12,775
According to Kyung Hee,
he isn't interested in his looks.

276
00:21:13,259 --> 00:21:15,541
I'm not so sure about that,

277
00:21:15,641 --> 00:21:18,175
but he's dyed his hair back to black.

278
00:21:18,275 --> 00:21:19,272
Really?

279
00:21:20,173 --> 00:21:21,206
I was worried...

280
00:21:21,311 --> 00:21:24,380
...I might come off as being nosy if
I asked about it directly to him.

281
00:21:25,579 --> 00:21:26,815
I see.

282
00:21:31,564 --> 00:21:34,573
I guess you're the one in trouble.

283
00:21:35,561 --> 00:21:36,366
What?

284
00:21:36,673 --> 00:21:38,913
Are you worried about something?

285
00:21:46,195 --> 00:21:49,286
You must not want to
share it with me. Sorry.

286
00:21:49,985 --> 00:21:51,276
Well...

287
00:21:54,106 --> 00:21:55,684
That's...

288
00:21:57,173 --> 00:22:00,784
Woo Young, I want to apply
for the field trip.

289
00:22:00,884 --> 00:22:01,899
Okay.

290
00:22:02,807 --> 00:22:04,388
Let's see.

291
00:22:05,529 --> 00:22:07,674
(List of Field Trip Applicants)

292
00:22:07,789 --> 00:22:09,103
Your name is Hyun Soo A, right?

293
00:22:09,591 --> 00:22:10,499
Yes.

294
00:22:12,782 --> 00:22:14,464
(Ko Ye Na, Kim Tae Hee,
Yoo Eun, Jang Won Ho,)

295
00:22:14,574 --> 00:22:16,992
(Lee Ji Hyo, Kim Sung Woon,
Jung Dong Won, Hyun Soo A)

296
00:22:17,363 --> 00:22:18,576
It's done.

297
00:22:18,676 --> 00:22:21,376
Thank you. Goodbye.

298
00:22:21,477 --> 00:22:22,483
Bye.

299
00:22:24,574 --> 00:22:26,688
Kyung Seok, are you here to apply...

300
00:22:31,460 --> 00:22:32,664
What's up?

301
00:22:32,764 --> 00:22:35,457
Don't tell me you're here
to call off the rent issue.

302
00:22:35,557 --> 00:22:36,974
I'm here to apply for the field trip.

303
00:22:37,874 --> 00:22:39,756
- To Kelun?
- Yes.

304
00:22:45,077 --> 00:22:46,488
Do better for your mother.

305
00:22:46,588 --> 00:22:48,390
That's my business, not yours.

306
00:22:52,674 --> 00:22:54,364
Are you mad at me?

307
00:22:57,273 --> 00:22:59,710
It's done, right? Bye.

308
00:23:05,096 --> 00:23:08,212
He's acting the opposite
from the way he seems.

309
00:23:14,103 --> 00:23:15,397
You like him,

310
00:23:15,497 --> 00:23:17,551
and he seems to like you too,

311
00:23:17,651 --> 00:23:19,346
so why do you have to give up?

312
00:23:21,941 --> 00:23:24,752
I think it's because I'm scared.

313
00:23:27,874 --> 00:23:30,682
He's beyond my league.

314
00:23:30,874 --> 00:23:32,360
He's too perfect for me.

315
00:23:32,460 --> 00:23:34,669
Still, you two like each other, so why?

316
00:23:37,349 --> 00:23:39,049
The thing is,

317
00:23:39,939 --> 00:23:42,572
a girl who's super pretty
has a crush on him.

318
00:23:43,356 --> 00:23:46,175
And everyone says that
they'd make a cute couple.

319
00:23:46,941 --> 00:23:51,349
As you know, I got plastic surgery
all over my face. If he dates me...

320
00:23:51,874 --> 00:23:54,689
...instead of that girl, what will
people say? I'm just so scared.

321
00:23:55,307 --> 00:23:56,904
I see.

322
00:23:58,798 --> 00:24:00,408
I must sound like an idiot.

323
00:24:03,674 --> 00:24:05,109
But still,

324
00:24:05,472 --> 00:24:07,788
what matters is the fact that
you two like each other,

325
00:24:07,888 --> 00:24:09,688
so don't think about other people.

326
00:24:12,501 --> 00:24:15,507
That's what everyone will say though.

327
00:24:16,797 --> 00:24:17,892
I understand.

328
00:24:17,992 --> 00:24:21,729
I'm sure many girls will feel
that way in your situation.

329
00:24:23,088 --> 00:24:24,598
I'm getting angry at the people...

330
00:24:24,707 --> 00:24:27,794
...who made you think that.

331
00:24:29,436 --> 00:24:30,924
I don't know the details,

332
00:24:31,025 --> 00:24:33,514
so I can't really give you advice.

333
00:24:33,607 --> 00:24:37,144
But perhaps, that pretty girl...

334
00:24:37,474 --> 00:24:41,256
isn't much different from you.

335
00:24:42,542 --> 00:24:47,049
I just don't want you to
have any regrets later on.

336
00:24:52,154 --> 00:24:53,651
You've applied for the
lab experience, right?

337
00:24:53,752 --> 00:24:54,461
Pardon?

338
00:24:59,718 --> 00:25:01,236
Let's eat.

339
00:25:02,432 --> 00:25:04,835
Have this too. Help yourself.

340
00:25:04,935 --> 00:25:06,930
Thank you for the food.

341
00:25:15,995 --> 00:25:17,380
Soo A may not be...

342
00:25:17,807 --> 00:25:20,885
...that different from me?

343
00:25:28,635 --> 00:25:30,132
Hi, Woo Young.

344
00:25:31,507 --> 00:25:33,323
I'm on my way home now.

345
00:25:33,407 --> 00:25:34,506
Mi Rae.

346
00:25:37,823 --> 00:25:38,723
My gosh.

347
00:25:38,807 --> 00:25:40,193
Good timing.

348
00:25:41,096 --> 00:25:42,702
Hello.

349
00:25:43,618 --> 00:25:45,110
Can we talk for a minute?

350
00:25:46,407 --> 00:25:47,707
Sure.

351
00:25:48,013 --> 00:25:51,016
I noticed that you haven't applied.
Have you forgotten about it?

352
00:25:52,707 --> 00:25:53,974
No.

353
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:57,823
I'm thinking of visiting my
family during summer break.

354
00:26:00,006 --> 00:26:01,306
But it's not for the whole summer.

355
00:26:01,393 --> 00:26:03,095
You can visit them after it's done.

356
00:26:05,973 --> 00:26:07,966
I just thought you'd definitely apply...

357
00:26:08,067 --> 00:26:10,076
...because you're very
interested in perfume.

358
00:26:10,171 --> 00:26:12,471
And most importantly, I think...

359
00:26:12,571 --> 00:26:15,074
...it'd be a good chance for you to
find out how suited you are...

360
00:26:15,174 --> 00:26:16,975
...to pursue a career in
the perfume industry.

361
00:26:18,677 --> 00:26:21,480
Besides, there may not be
another opportunity to get...

362
00:26:21,580 --> 00:26:24,074
...a first-hand experience at a
perfume lab until you graduate.

363
00:26:29,088 --> 00:26:31,790
Can I still apply for the program?

364
00:26:32,040 --> 00:26:34,974
Of course. I'll add your
name to the list right away.

365
00:26:37,073 --> 00:26:38,964
- Shall we go?
- Yes.

366
00:26:40,866 --> 00:26:42,367
Wait, Woo Young.

367
00:26:44,870 --> 00:26:46,174
Thank you.

368
00:26:47,574 --> 00:26:50,475
Then are you free on Wednesday?

369
00:26:50,876 --> 00:26:51,623
Sorry?

370
00:26:51,707 --> 00:26:53,907
Let's watch a movie. We can
get a discount that day.

371
00:26:55,481 --> 00:26:57,683
Then I'll let Hyun Jung know as well.

372
00:26:58,674 --> 00:26:59,974
Just the two of us.

373
00:27:02,474 --> 00:27:03,908
I have something to tell you.

374
00:27:06,474 --> 00:27:07,741
Okay.

375
00:27:08,841 --> 00:27:10,141
Let's go.

376
00:27:17,600 --> 00:27:19,034
I've gained a bit of weight.

377
00:27:50,941 --> 00:27:52,508
Hey, wait.

378
00:27:56,228 --> 00:27:57,528
Dong Won.

379
00:27:59,322 --> 00:28:00,656
I heard...

380
00:28:02,681 --> 00:28:04,679
...that canned tuna is high in sodium.

381
00:28:04,774 --> 00:28:06,285
You shouldn't give it to cats.

382
00:28:06,385 --> 00:28:08,287
If you still want to, you
should rinse it in water...

383
00:28:08,387 --> 00:28:10,541
...to remove the oil and sodium
before giving it to them.

384
00:28:12,357 --> 00:28:13,959
Hey, Soo A!

385
00:28:14,259 --> 00:28:15,874
Oh, hi.

386
00:28:17,062 --> 00:28:18,656
- Have you eaten yet?
- Yes. What about you?

387
00:28:18,740 --> 00:28:20,341
I've eaten too.

388
00:28:31,636 --> 00:28:33,041
Hi, Mi Rae.

389
00:28:33,137 --> 00:28:34,838
- Hi.
- Hi.

390
00:28:35,938 --> 00:28:37,549
Let's sit over there.

391
00:28:37,950 --> 00:28:39,241
Hi.

392
00:28:39,373 --> 00:28:40,673
Hi.

393
00:28:43,855 --> 00:28:45,474
Do you guys still work there part-time?

394
00:28:46,440 --> 00:28:48,160
No, we quit.

395
00:28:48,474 --> 00:28:49,874
Kyung Seok too?

396
00:28:50,262 --> 00:28:51,507
Yes.

397
00:28:54,774 --> 00:28:56,308
Hi, Kyung Seok.

398
00:29:01,336 --> 00:29:03,242
I heard you quit your part-time job.

399
00:29:08,753 --> 00:29:11,148
He shouldn't have gotten involved
in that thing. I feel bad.

400
00:29:21,941 --> 00:29:23,008
Nice to meet you all.

401
00:29:23,106 --> 00:29:25,408
I'm Chief Director Lee Soo Hyun.

402
00:29:25,607 --> 00:29:27,606
This is Ms. Yun Soo Kyeong,

403
00:29:27,709 --> 00:29:28,916
who will be your guide.

404
00:29:29,111 --> 00:29:31,378
Hello, everyone. It's
nice to meet you all.

405
00:29:34,040 --> 00:29:36,153
While getting your first-hand
experience at our lab,

406
00:29:36,272 --> 00:29:39,175
you'll also learn about theories
and the history of perfume.

407
00:29:39,270 --> 00:29:41,571
If you have any questions or suggestions,

408
00:29:41,667 --> 00:29:43,476
you can speak to Ms. Yun here.

409
00:29:43,570 --> 00:29:45,237
- Okay.
- Okay.

410
00:29:47,607 --> 00:29:49,141
Yes, come in.

411
00:29:52,195 --> 00:29:53,595
Why did you come to school today?

412
00:29:53,680 --> 00:29:54,674
I'm taking a summer class.

413
00:29:54,795 --> 00:29:56,495
Oh, I see.

414
00:29:56,973 --> 00:29:58,586
What brings you here?

415
00:29:58,671 --> 00:30:01,205
There's something I want to tell you.

416
00:30:01,600 --> 00:30:02,808
Me?

417
00:30:03,507 --> 00:30:05,270
I'm not an eloquent speaker,

418
00:30:05,404 --> 00:30:08,507
so I wrote down what I want to tell you.

419
00:30:19,559 --> 00:30:21,060
Okay, bye.

420
00:30:32,340 --> 00:30:34,407
Dear Woo Young,

421
00:30:34,727 --> 00:30:37,074
I'm Kwon Yoon Byul in second year.

422
00:30:37,169 --> 00:30:39,571
I have a crush on you.

423
00:30:39,674 --> 00:30:41,673
You're very responsible and
have a strong sense of ethics.

424
00:30:41,773 --> 00:30:42,974
You also respect women.

425
00:30:43,075 --> 00:30:45,308
I like everything about you.

426
00:30:45,774 --> 00:30:49,381
I wrote this letter because I'm
too shy to tell you in person.

427
00:30:49,581 --> 00:30:51,583
With warm regards, Kwon Yoon Byul.

428
00:30:51,683 --> 00:30:54,241
Shy, my foot. She's so brave.

429
00:30:55,340 --> 00:30:57,556
My gosh, what should I do about this?

430
00:31:02,628 --> 00:31:05,162
First, go ahead and smell
the undiluted scents.

431
00:31:05,292 --> 00:31:07,859
Then please write down which scents...

432
00:31:07,965 --> 00:31:09,566
...are in the perfume I gave you guys.

433
00:31:20,666 --> 00:31:22,660
Because I've been smelling
all these different scents,

434
00:31:22,758 --> 00:31:23,992
I can't even smell anything now.

435
00:31:24,106 --> 00:31:27,319
You'll have to reset your sense
of smell here and there.

436
00:31:27,419 --> 00:31:29,007
You can either take a short break...

437
00:31:29,121 --> 00:31:32,224
...or try smelling coffee beans here.
It'll help.

438
00:31:55,150 --> 00:31:57,449
I think it has these scents.

439
00:31:59,651 --> 00:32:02,654
You're right. You guessed every
scent in the perfume correctly.

440
00:32:04,756 --> 00:32:06,358
That's impressive.

441
00:32:06,658 --> 00:32:09,828
Are you Kang Mi Rae? You're the
one who sent us that perfume.

442
00:32:09,941 --> 00:32:11,842
Everyone in our lab loved that perfume.

443
00:32:11,930 --> 00:32:13,832
We've been wanting to meet you in person.

444
00:32:14,633 --> 00:32:16,332
Thank you for the compliment.

445
00:32:16,735 --> 00:32:19,905
My gosh, you're a perfume expert.

446
00:32:41,907 --> 00:32:44,241
It wasn't supposed to rain today.

447
00:32:51,273 --> 00:32:52,573
Woo Young.

448
00:32:54,073 --> 00:32:55,473
Woo Young.

449
00:32:56,274 --> 00:32:58,443
Wait, Woo Young.

450
00:32:59,644 --> 00:33:01,746
What were you pondering?

451
00:33:02,841 --> 00:33:04,549
Well, just some things.

452
00:33:07,207 --> 00:33:08,808
Have you had dinner yet?

453
00:33:08,920 --> 00:33:11,808
Oh, right. Come to think of it,
I didn't even have lunch today.

454
00:33:11,923 --> 00:33:14,708
Are you saying you didn't eat all day?

455
00:33:14,826 --> 00:33:16,541
That's bad.

456
00:33:16,841 --> 00:33:18,241
Thanks for your concern.

457
00:33:21,433 --> 00:33:22,834
Well...

458
00:33:23,106 --> 00:33:26,438
Do you want to grab dinner with me?

459
00:33:26,838 --> 00:33:28,340
Sure, what should we eat?

460
00:33:29,140 --> 00:33:31,543
Then... Since it's a hot day,

461
00:33:31,643 --> 00:33:33,445
let's just go somewhere close.

462
00:33:33,745 --> 00:33:35,013
- Sure.
- Great.

463
00:33:39,901 --> 00:33:41,002
- Welcome.
- Hello.

464
00:33:41,087 --> 00:33:42,788
- Hi.
- You can sit over there.

465
00:33:52,089 --> 00:33:53,297
He's still here.

466
00:33:53,384 --> 00:33:55,796
He's a part-timer now, not the owner.

467
00:33:55,905 --> 00:33:57,002
Really?

468
00:34:00,173 --> 00:34:02,407
- He must've gone bankrupt.
- Exactly.

469
00:34:03,608 --> 00:34:04,908
Hey.

470
00:34:05,106 --> 00:34:06,506
What do you want? Beer?

471
00:34:08,613 --> 00:34:10,315
I don't think I'm good with perfume.

472
00:34:10,407 --> 00:34:11,917
I can't even smell anything anymore.

473
00:34:12,006 --> 00:34:14,219
I enjoyed it. I wasn't
interested in perfume,

474
00:34:14,319 --> 00:34:15,520
- but it was really fun.
- I know.

475
00:34:15,640 --> 00:34:17,207
- Right?
- Yes.

476
00:34:18,023 --> 00:34:19,724
Mi Rae, you looked really excited.

477
00:34:19,824 --> 00:34:21,826
You must really like perfume.

478
00:34:27,674 --> 00:34:29,601
- I'm hungry.
- But you already ate.

479
00:34:29,701 --> 00:34:32,307
Why are you sitting here
alone like a loner?

480
00:34:33,071 --> 00:34:34,907
I was a loner all my life.

481
00:34:35,006 --> 00:34:37,008
What would you have done without me?

482
00:34:37,108 --> 00:34:38,507
I know, right?

483
00:34:39,010 --> 00:34:40,008
Do you guys all want beer?

484
00:34:40,111 --> 00:34:41,713
- Beer sounds good.
- Sure.

485
00:34:42,514 --> 00:34:45,075
Kyung Seok, what are you doing there?

486
00:34:45,907 --> 00:34:47,241
You should go.

487
00:34:47,740 --> 00:34:50,007
I can't be bothered. I'm going to
leave after I'm done with this.

488
00:34:50,121 --> 00:34:53,224
Kyung Seok, get over here.

489
00:34:53,340 --> 00:34:55,427
- Kyung Seok.
- Come on.

490
00:34:55,527 --> 00:34:58,223
- Come sit here.
- Just go.

491
00:34:58,307 --> 00:35:00,340
You're practically
volunteering to be a loner.

492
00:35:01,032 --> 00:35:03,935
I thought things were getting
better, but you're doing it again.

493
00:35:06,137 --> 00:35:08,640
- Kyung Seok.
- Come on.

494
00:35:08,740 --> 00:35:11,441
Gosh, he's so cold-hearted.

495
00:35:21,252 --> 00:35:22,540
Is there something going on?

496
00:35:24,856 --> 00:35:26,758
There's something on my mind.

497
00:35:27,640 --> 00:35:28,974
What is it?

498
00:35:34,161 --> 00:35:37,573
Well, the thing is, someone confessed...

499
00:35:38,570 --> 00:35:40,241
...their feelings for me today.

500
00:35:40,338 --> 00:35:41,239
What?

501
00:35:42,240 --> 00:35:43,742
Why are you so startled?

502
00:35:44,442 --> 00:35:45,443
Is it that shocking?

503
00:35:45,543 --> 00:35:47,640
No, it's not shocking.

504
00:35:48,207 --> 00:35:50,515
Gosh, you're really popular.

505
00:35:50,615 --> 00:35:52,017
I'm not popular.

506
00:35:54,719 --> 00:35:56,307
What are you going to do?

507
00:35:58,106 --> 00:36:02,239
I'm just thinking about how
I'm going to turn her down.

508
00:36:04,262 --> 00:36:06,272
Have you already made up your mind?

509
00:36:06,357 --> 00:36:08,967
Yes, I can't suddenly like someone...

510
00:36:09,067 --> 00:36:11,169
...just because that person likes me.

511
00:36:13,407 --> 00:36:16,041
I guess you're very clear
with what you want.

512
00:36:16,241 --> 00:36:18,043
I just know what kind of women I like.

513
00:36:20,340 --> 00:36:22,547
Don't be too harsh though.

514
00:36:24,049 --> 00:36:28,453
Some people say you should be
cold when you reject someone.

515
00:36:28,674 --> 00:36:31,241
But if she's a decent person,

516
00:36:31,556 --> 00:36:35,927
she'd appreciate it if
you reject her politely.

517
00:36:38,029 --> 00:36:39,464
I guess you're right.

518
00:36:39,740 --> 00:36:43,274
I feel like it'll scar her for
life if the guy she likes...

519
00:36:44,340 --> 00:36:45,970
...says harsh things to her.

520
00:36:47,173 --> 00:36:49,774
That's never happened to me, but still.

521
00:36:50,875 --> 00:36:52,277
You must know well even
without experience...

522
